flowchart TD
    Start([New Email Arrives]) --> Extract[Extract sender, subject, body, domain]

    Extract --> R0{Rule 0:<br/>Learned Sender?}
    R0 -->|KEEP rule| KEEP([KEEP])
    R0 -->|DELETE rule| DELETE([DELETE])
    R0 -->|No rule| R05

    R05{Rule 0.5:<br/>Learned Subject<br/>DELETE match?}
    R05 -->|Yes| DELETE
    R05 -->|No| R1

    R1{Rule 1:<br/>Protected Domain?}
    R1 -->|Yes| MOVE([MOVE to Protected])
    R1 -->|No| R2

    R2{Rule 2:<br/>Personally<br/>Addressed?}
    R2 -->|Name in subject<br/>or greeting in body| KEEP
    R2 -->|No| R3

    R3{Rule 3:<br/>Org Tags?<br/>MM, HRO, CUS, ToXX}
    R3 -->|Yes| KEEP
    R3 -->|No| R4

    R4{Rule 4:<br/>VIP Keywords?<br/>thesis, deadline...}
    R4 -->|Yes| KEEP
    R4 -->|No| R5

    R5{Rule 5:<br/>RE: Reply?}
    R5 -->|Yes| KEEP
    R5 -->|No| R6

    R6{Rule 6:<br/>FW: Forward?}
    R6 -->|Yes| KEEP
    R6 -->|No| R7

    R7{Rule 7:<br/>Known Spam<br/>Sender?}
    R7 -->|Yes| DELETE
    R7 -->|No| R8

    R8{Rule 8:<br/>Sender Pattern?<br/>noreply, marketing...}
    R8 -->|Yes| DELETE
    R8 -->|No| R9

    R9{Rule 9:<br/>Subject Pattern?<br/>digest, newsletter...}
    R9 -->|Yes| DELETE
    R9 -->|No| R10

    R10{Rule 10:<br/>LLM Enabled?}
    R10 -->|Yes| LLM[Call LLM via CallLLM]
    R10 -->|No| REVIEW([MOVE to Review])

    LLM --> LLMResult{LLM Says?}
    LLMResult -->|DELETE| DELETE
    LLMResult -->|KEEP| KEEP
    LLMResult -->|Unclear / Error| REVIEW
